{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_21932.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":104301,"motion":1,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story07","nameNarration":"Kuroe","narration":"\"I get the feeling that you already know this, but...\"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"\"A weak Magical Girl like me,@with my will to live and@my belief in my wish fading away,@was trapped in the fear of becoming a Witch.@I had no choice but to spend my days @trying to scrape up Grief Seeds just to survive.\""},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"white","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}],"nameNarration":"Kuroe","narration":"\"...But Magical Girls like Tamaki-san,@with a sturdy hope planted in their hearts,@kept fighting to protect Magical Girls@and humans alike from Witches.\"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"black","item":[{"iPhoneXScale":1.0,"path":"resource/scenario/img/chapter10/102003_iroha_3rd.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/chapter10/102003_iroha_3rd.jpg","visible":"hide"}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"item":[{"iPhoneXScale":1.0,"path":"resource/scenario/img/chapter8/101802_manypuela.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}]},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/chapter8/101802_manypuela.jpg","visible":"hide"}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"item":[{"iPhoneXScale":1.0,"path":"resource/scenario/img/chapter9/memoria_1256.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}]},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/chapter9/memoria_1256.jpg","visible":"hide"}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"item":[{"iPhoneXScale":1.0,"path":"resource/scenario/img/chapter10/102005_magicalgirl3.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}]},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"Kuroe","narration":"\"And thanks to what she and her friends told me...\"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"item":[{"iPhoneXScale":1.0,"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter1/103101_kimochi_encount.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter1/103101_kimochi_encount.jpg","visible":"hide"}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"item":[{"iPhoneXScale":1.0,"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter4/102504_sapphire_iroha2.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}]},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter4/102504_sapphire_iroha2.jpg","visible":"hide"}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter8/102909_stone_gather.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}]},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter8/102909_stone_gather.jpg","visible":"hide"}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter12/103305_mikazuki.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}]},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter12/103305_mikazuki.jpg","visible":"hide"}]},{"nameNarration":"Kuroe","narration":"\"I realized that even if@our souls are in a different place,@as long as Magical Girls hold on tight to hope,@we can become something that lets us stay human.\"","narrationEffect":"in"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51160_tower_kuroe/memoria_1743.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"Kuroe","narration":"\"I was never able to do that myself, but...\"","narrationCoverOpacity":100.0,"narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"\"It's because she called my name@that I didn't lose sight of who I am.\""},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_21932.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104301,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"nameNarration":"Kuroe","narration":"\"Magical Girls can absolutely kill people,@and that's a way of saving people, too.\"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104301,"motion":300}],"narration":"\"But Tamaki-san might be able to save@even the ones who probably deserve to be killed.\""},{"narration":"\"She could change people@that I can't do anything about.\""},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104301,"motion":1}],"narration":"\"I don't want to hurt anybody@that she might've been able to help...\""},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":104301,"pos":0}],"narrationEffect":"out"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":390201,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"Tamaki Iroha-san sounds like the type of Magical@Girl who put her money where her mouth was."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":104301}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"...She really did."},{"chara":[{"id":104301},{"id":390201,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"While I was talking to Yuu-san..."},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"...I noticed that the emptiness inside her feels@like it's pulling my soul in..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104301}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"That same type of feeling you get looking over the@edge of a cliff, like it's going to drag you down..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":104301}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"It's in the complete opposite direction, but just@like with Yuu-san's emptiness..."},{"chara":[{"id":104301}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"...I was drawn towards the hope in Tamaki-san's@soul."},{"chara":[{"id":390201,"motion":300},{"id":104301,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"...It would seem that we're both nobodies..."},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"...charmed by hope and curses, respectively."},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"You don't have to get so logical about it."},{"chara":[{"id":104301}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"If you're familiar with Yuu-san, you should@understand..."},{"chara":[{"id":104301}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"...that the fact I've changed is proof of hope."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104301,"lipSynch":0},{"id":390201,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":104301,"lipSynch":1,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Maybe John-san..."},{"chara":[{"id":104301}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"...really did do something unforgivable."},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"But I definitely saw the weak, cowardly parts of@myself in him."},{"chara":[{"id":104301}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Something like you and I could empathize with."},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"motion":400}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"There was definitely hope that he could change!"},{"chara":[{"id":104301}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Just like we can!"},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"bgmFadeOut":3000,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":390201}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":390201,"motion":100},{"id":104301,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"...I appreciate the sentiment."},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"I think that I can more or less understand..."},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"...you and Tamaki Iroha-san."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"..."},{"bgm":"bgm05_event07","chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":104301,"lipSynch":1,"motion":100},{"id":390201,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Why are you doing this, anyway?"},{"chara":[{"id":104301}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Do you honestly think it's \"right\"..."},{"chara":[{"id":104301}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"...to kill somebody because you decided that@they were a bad person?"},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"You'd mentioned something about selling bodies@earlier..."},{"chara":[{"id":104301}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"...but that can't possibly be your goal, right?"},{"chara":[{"id":104301}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"I don't think you'd be using Yuu-san for your@own convenience like that."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":390201,"lipSynch":0}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_032.exp3.json","id":390201,"lipSynch":1,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"You're giving me too much credit..."},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"Yuu is helping me and getting nothing in return..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":390201}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"...so I am, in fact, using her for my own@convenience..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":390201,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"But as you said, it's not about selling the bodies—@that's simply a bonus."},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"They'd go to waste otherwise."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":390201,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"It is true that the names I put on my list are bad@people."},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"And it is also true that I can help myself by killing@those bad people."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":390201,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"Would it add any more credibility if I told you..."},{"chara":[{"id":390201}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"...that I'm able to determine who's a \"bad person\"@because of a Magical Girl's wish?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":104301,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Your mother's wish..."},{"chara":[{"id":390201,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"Indeed... I'm not sure where to start."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":390201}],"nameRight":"Shii","textRight":"This might get a bit...lengthy."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
